-- Meister Rejects Europe Deposit Guarantee, Euro am Sonntag Says
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-06-06T18:31:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-06/meister-rejects-europe-deposit-guarantee-euro-am-sonntag-says.html
Michael Meister, the deputy floor
leader of German Chancellor  Angela Merkel ’s Christian Democratic
Union party, rejected proposals for a European fund for deposit
guarantees,  Euro am Sonntag  said in a preview of a story that
will be published tomorrow, citing an interview with Meister.  Such a fund would be a “hidden transfer union” at German
taxpayers’ expense, Meister said, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
